Content: And also a lack of flat screens streaming 4k+, I have heard that they are streaming some matches in 4k, but that‚Äôs only on streaming platforms and cable at 1080p.

Author: glassesofwater

Author: glassesofwater
Content: Spidey Cams are fun as just ridiculously expensive.

Author: glassesofwater
Content: Sky cams in soccer would go a long way, but I think when Sports matures then art will mature. Sport isn‚Äôt as critical thinking intensive and is definitely more communal than an artistic movie. It‚Äôs just the money is there but they wouldn‚Äôt reinvest it back into the production.

Author: anrinobel
Content:
üëã Hey folks,
I‚Äôm a  .NET Developer ‚Äî I do backend, frontend, sometimes both, sometimes just fixing that one weird bug nobody else wants to touch. Flexible is my middle name.

üáÆüá© Problem is: in Indonesia, job hunting feels like an MMORPG quest. Companies want a god-tier dev who can code, design, do DevOps, summon dragons, and maybe even brew coffee at the same time. ü§∑‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è Reality check: I‚Äôm human. Not a demigod. But a pretty decent one.

My toolkit:

- Backend with .NET / C# (APIs, services, you name it)
- Frontend with React/Angular (making UIs look less like 2005 websites)
- Databases: SQL Server, PostgreSQL, MySQL (queries don‚Äôt scare me)
- Remote-friendly, team-friendly, meme-friendly.

So if you need a fullstack developer who delivers but keeps it human, hit me up. If not, we can still game together while I pretend to refactor my code. üòé
